## ⚡ 9. Common Errors & Fixes

### ❌ Permission Denied

```bash
chmod 600 key.pem
```

---

### ❌ Key Not Found

```bash
ssh -i /full/path/key.pem ubuntu@<ip>
```

---

### ❌ Wrong Username

* Ubuntu → `ubuntu`
* Amazon Linux → `ec2-user`

